    <stitle>13 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON RTLO-14613 - INSTALL - OUTPUT YOKE</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="4">
        <title>OUTPUT YOKE</title>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>Replacement of the seal and slinger must be completed prior to yoke or flange installation.</para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install speedometer gear or spacer on the output shaft (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13027r9">Figure 279</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f13027r9" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g13027r9" filename="../figg13/G13027r9.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 279. Install Speedometer Gear or Spacer on Output Shaft</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Place the output yoke or flange onto the output shaft (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13027s0">Figure 280</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f13027s0" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g13027s0" filename="../figg13/G13027s0.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 280. Place Output Yoke or Flange onto Output Shaft</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the washer and output nut onto the output shaft (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13027s1">Figure 281</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f13027s1" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g13027s1" filename="../figg13/G13027s1.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 281. Install Washer and Output Nut onto Output Shaft</caption>
        </figure>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>It will be necessary to temporarily lock the transmission in two gears by moving the sliding
                    clutch into gear for the final torque procedure.
                </para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Complete installation process by tightening the output shaft nut to 450 to 500 ft-lbs. (610
                to 678 N&#183; m) (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13027s2">Figure 282</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f13027s2" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g13027s2" filename="../figg13/G13027s2.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 282. Tighten Output Shaft Nut</caption>
        </figure>
    </svcproc>
